{"about_the_game":"Loverowind is a very short experience about the wind of spring.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSimilar to my previous game Pluviophile, you collect flowers, and use them on the altars to reveal a poem. But this time you move much faster, unless the circles of light roaming in the world don't catch you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThen in order to move fast again, you have to collect orbs which grant you speed for a limited time. After you unlock all the altars in the level, a huge sphere appears, and you need to catch it so the gate to proceed to the next level opens again.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe core aspect of this game is the atmosphere. It is recommended for those who mostly seek to experience the mood.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSave progression: The game saves your progression at the beginning of each level.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rock n' Roll","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625960/b524f76d797aaf0e3e0f0f2a17b6cd725cb73b8d.jpg"},{"name":"Jump Around","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625960/b524f76d797aaf0e3e0f0f2a17b6cd725cb73b8d.jpg"},{"name":"Rise and Shine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625960/b524f76d797aaf0e3e0f0f2a17b6cd725cb73b8d.jpg"},{"name":"Emerson","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625960/b524f76d797aaf0e3e0f0f2a17b6cd725cb73b8d.jpg"},{"name":"Green Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625960/b524f76d797aaf0e3e0f0f2a17b6cd725cb73b8d.jpg"},{"name":"Dylan","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625960/b524f76d797aaf0e3e0f0f2a17b6cd725cb73b8d.jpg"},{"name":"Dust in the Wind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625960/b524f76d797aaf0e3e0f0f2a17b6cd725cb73b8d.jpg"}],"total":7},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass